  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with high horseshoe anal fistula will be randomized to one of two equal group:&#xD;
      treatment group will have decompression and drainage seton and control group will undergo&#xD;
      cutting seton.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
